name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Tyrone GRANT, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Tyrone GRANT, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 15th of December, 2011, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

casebody.head_matter:
34 A.3d 66
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Tyrone GRANT, Petitioner.
No. 86 EM 2011.
Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
Dec. 15, 2011.
